All TypeScript files **must** use kebab-case for their file names.

✔ Use only lowercase letters, numbers and dashes (e.g. `runs-table.tsx`, `auth-form.ts`).
✖ Do NOT use camelCase, PascalCase, or underscores (e.g. `RunsTable.tsx` or `auth_Form.tsx`).
